txt.en: Supplies are running low in Ugrukhôr's encampment, west of Barad Angarth.\n\nYou should seek out and destroy the supplies.

'Greetings, friend. As you reported, it seems that Ugrukhôr's forces are running low on supplies. If we were to destroy the few supplies that remain, we might sufficiently enrage the Orcs into attacking Gothmog's forces. And wouldn't that be a pity?\n\n'Go forth and destroy the supplies that you find, and we will see if I am right.'
You destroyed some of the supplies in Ugrukhôr's camp.\n\nYou should return to Dolenthol and inform him of your victory.
Supplies are running low in Ugrukhôr's encampment, but they might always run lower....

'With the supplies destroyed, the Orcs become more and more aggressive. In point of fact, they may begin to raid Gothmog's encampment to seize the supplies they now lack!\n\n'Well done, I say. Well done to both of us.'
